<!---------------Header Row ^ ---------------------->
<div class='row'>
    <div class='col-xs-3'>
         <div class='col-sm-12' style="margin-top: -200px ;">
                    <img src="/FDEZBEATS.jpg" height="200px" width="200px" class = "rounded-img">
             </div>
             <div class="col-sm-12">
            <h3 style="font-weight: bold ; color: #14c30e "><%= @username %></h3>
            <p> Bacon ipsum dolor amet pork belly culpa shankle, capicola beef turducken laboris frankfurter nulla. Kielbasa reprehenderit laboris, ut hamburger biltong minim ham et. Aute cow spare ribs nulla voluptate. Commodo ground round shank meatball pork loin consectetur lorem tempor labore duis jerky beef ribs. Ea consequat dolor ut, ad adipisicing kevin turkey. Proident chicken pork fugiat sirloin biltong, non ham hock. Anim ex culpa tongue jerky consectetur.</p>
            
            </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class='col-xs-6'>
        <%= render '/components/post_form' %>
       <br><br>
        
        <% for @p in @posts %>
        <div class="panel panel-default post-panel">
          <div class="panel-body row">
            <div class= "col-sm-1">
              <img src="/FDEZBEATS.jpg" class="rounded-img" height="50px" width="50px"></img>
            </div>
                <div class="col-sm-11">
                  <p class="post-title"><span class="post-owner"><%= User.find(@p.user_id).username %></span> - <span class="post-creation"><%= @p.created_at.to_formatted_s(:short) %></span> </p>
                  <p class="post-content"><%= @p.content %></p>
                </div>
                
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                      <p class="post-link">
                        
                        
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-flash g-links" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-heart-empty g-links " aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-record g-links" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-floppy-disk g-links" aria-hidden="true"></span>
                        <a href="">View Conversation</a>
                        </p>
                    </div>
            
          
                </div>
            </div>
           <% end %>
       </div>
  
    <div class='col-xs-3'>
        <%= render '/components/follow_button', :user => User.find_by_username(params[:id]) %>
         <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-body">
             <h5 style="color: grey; font-size: 125%;">Who to follow</h5>
                 <% for @u in @tofollow do%>
                 <p style="font-weight: bold; opacity: 0.85;" ><a href="/user/<%= @u.username %>>"><%= @u.username %></a></p>
                 <%end%>
                </div>
          </div>
        <div class="panel panel-default">
          <div class="panel-body">
               <h5 style="color: grey; font-size: 125%;">Trends</h5>
              <a href=""> Trend #1</a><br> 
                <span style = "color: grey ;">31k post</span><br>
            <a href=""> Trend #2</a><br> 
                <span style = "color: grey ;">21k post</span><br>
                 <a href=""> Trend #3</a><br> 
                <span style = "color: grey ;">11k post</span><br>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>




